<h1>Algolia Search example app</h1>

<h3>Installation</h3>

<ol>
  <li><code>bundle install</code></li>
  <li><code>bundle exec rake db:migrate</code></li>
  <li><code>rails generate figaro:install</code></li>
  <li>Create your <code>config/application.yml</code> based on <code>config/application.example.yml</code></li>
  <li><code>bundle exec rake db:seed</code></li>
  <li><code>bundle exec rails server</code></li>
  <li>Enjoy your <code>http://localhost:3000</code>!</li>
</ol>


